This artifact vendors the "subagent-driven-development" skill from obra/superpowers.

Vendored files (upstream paths):
  - skills/subagent-driven-development/SKILL.md
  - skills/subagent-driven-development/implementer-prompt.md
  - skills/subagent-driven-development/task-reviewer-prompt.md
  - skills/subagent-driven-development/scripts/{task-brief,review-package,sdd-workspace}

The SKILL.md body is upstream-verbatim; a short "Patronus note" block was
prepended at the top mapping the `superpowers:` sibling cross-references to the
corresponding Patronus artifacts (writing-plans, executing-plans, tdd,
dispatching-parallel-agents) and marking the un-vendored siblings
(requesting-code-review, finishing-a-development-branch, using-git-worktrees)
optional. The scripts/ helpers were audited before shipping: they perform only
git reads and file writes (no network access, no destructive operations).

